{"type": "article", "id": 19330, "title": "大理石制的桌面器皿", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-18T07:30:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606153737plWrmCe5PY4Nzu9O.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t纽约的工作室 Apparatus 新推出了这套桌面器皿，包括蜡烛灯、烛台和果盘。蜡烛灯和果盘的底座采用产自意大利的大理石，有黑白两色，天然的纹路显示出典雅和质感。果盘中间带有一个可取出的黄铜碗，方便承载和清洗食物。黄铜制作的烛台上有一个瓷制的半圆拱顶，顶端的圆孔用来散开燃香后的烟。三者都是用细长的底座拖着球形的容器，配合大理石纹和黄铜材料，古典而庄重。售价 780 美元起，<a href=\"http://apparatusstudio.com/product-category/objects/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145840hHK3I4ZqNsPwongm.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"1080\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145841dTp6Stm5vqZ31jx9.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145841nT9sVhtacbMuSCIU.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145841xkCudWFoEDawlXU7.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145842FigQuoe9rEHfp6Dl.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726145842hMUI2lP5FgELTtmJ.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"543\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.50277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}